{"title":"Vue基础入门","uid":"3a13b25df3ae48dbca78c649405861eb","slug":"Vue/Vue基础入门","date":"2022-09-01T13:30:00.000Z","updated":"2022-09-01T15:36:09.318Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue/Vue基础入门.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Vue-js基础入门\"><a href=\"#Vue-js基础入门\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue.js基础入门\"></a>Vue.js基础入门</h1><h2 id=\"1⃣️-什么是Vue\"><a href=\"#1⃣️-什么是Vue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1⃣️ 什么是Vue\"></a>1⃣️ 什么是Vue</h2><p>​\tVue读音类似View，是一套用于构建用户界面的渐进式框架与其他大型框架（Angular、React…）相比,Vue被设计为可以自底向上逐层应用。而其他大型框架需要一开始就对项目的技术方案进行强制性的要求，Vue则更灵活，我们既可以选择Vue来开发一个全新项目，也可以将Vue引入到一个现有的项目中。</p>\n<p>​\tVue的数据驱动是通过MVVM（Model-View-ViewModel）的模式来实现的，基本工作原理如下图所示：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/1.png\" alt=\"image-20220901214716518\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"2⃣️-Vue的优势\"><a href=\"#2⃣️-Vue的优势\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2⃣️ Vue的优势\"></a>2⃣️ Vue的优势</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>前端主流的框架有Angular、React、<strong>Vue</strong>。</p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>轻量级</li>\n<li>数据绑定（数据双向绑定。）</li>\n<li>指令 （v-for列表渲染、v-if条件渲染、v-bind动态绑定指令。）</li>\n<li>插件 （对框架的功能进行扩展，通过MyPlugin.install完成插件的编写，简单配置后就可以全局使用。）</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"3⃣️-Vue开发环境\"><a href=\"#3⃣️-Vue开发环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3⃣️ Vue开发环境\"></a>3⃣️ Vue开发环境</h2><ol>\n<li>VS Code编辑器</li>\n<li>git-bash命令工具</li>\n<li>Node.js环境</li>\n<li>npm包管理工具 （npm的服务器在国外，使用npm下载软件包的速度犹如龟速，所以解决办法要么换国内镜像，要么用vpn。）</li>\n<li>Chrome浏览器和vue-devtools扩展</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"4⃣️-webpack-打包工具\"><a href=\"#4⃣️-webpack-打包工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4⃣️ webpack 打包工具\"></a>4⃣️ webpack 打包工具</h2><h3 id=\"1-安装webpack\"><a href=\"#1-安装webpack\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.安装webpack\"></a>1.安装webpack</h3><p>命令行执行下面命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install webpack@4.27.x webpack-cli@3.x -g</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>这里其实我也不知道为什么课本一定要这个版本？？？</strong></p>\n<p><strong>webpack-cli是脚手架工具 “-g”表示全局安装。</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><blockquote>\n<p>我安装的时候就遇到了权限问题，只需要在终端输入如下命令就可以了</p></blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo s</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-webpack简单使用\"><a href=\"#2-webpack简单使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.webpack简单使用\"></a>2.webpack简单使用</h3><ol>\n<li>创建一个vue\\chapter\\demo01\\demo02目录。</li>\n<li>在demo02目录中创建example.js文件，文件内编辑如下代码：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">function add(a,b)&#123;\n    return a + b\n&#125;\nconsole.log(add(1,2)) &#x2F;&#x2F;a&#x3D;1,b&#x3D;2</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>上面的代码是计算显示a b两个数字之和，会在控制台中输出计算的结果。</strong></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>用终端在demo02目录下执行下面的命令（打包操作）：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cmd\" data-language=\"cmd\"><code class=\"language-cmd\">webpack example.js -o app.js</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>上面的命令执行后会编译example.js文件，将编译好的结果保存为app.js文件。</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><blockquote>\n<p>但是我非常不幸运，我的node.js版本是17.9.0，回车之后抛出了异常（error:03000086:digital envelope routines::initialization error）。</p>\n<p>原因：node.js V17版本中最近发布的OpenSSL3.0，而OpenSSL3.0对允许算法和密钥大小增加了严格的限制，可能会对生态系统造成一些影响。</p>\n<p>在node.js V17以前一些可以正常运行的的应用程序，在 V17 版本就可能会抛出异常。</p>\n<p>我的解决办法：</p>\n<p>使用npm安装n (node版本管理n)来达到降级的目的。命令如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install -g n #安装n</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">n stable #安装稳定版本</code></pre>\n\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>创建example.html文件，引入app.js文件。html代码如下：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;app.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>在浏览器中打开example.html，按F12查看控制台即可看到a+b的结果(3)。</li>\n</ol>\n","feature":true,"text":"Vue.js基础入门1⃣️ 什么是Vue​ Vue读音类似View，是一套用于构建用户界面的渐进式框架与其他大型框架（Angular、React…）相比,Vue被设计为可以自底向上逐层应用。而其他大型框架需要一开始就对项目的技术方案进行强制性的要求，Vue则更灵活，我们既可以选择Vu...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"计算机","slug":"计算机","count":5,"path":"api/categories/计算机.json"},{"name":"Vue","slug":"计算机/Vue","count":1,"path":"api/categories/计算机/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":8,"path":"api/tags/笔记.json"},{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Vue-js%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Vue.js基础入门</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E2%83%A3%EF%B8%8F-%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AFVue\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1⃣️ 什么是Vue</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E2%83%A3%EF%B8